item.title: Green Medical Scrub
item.description: Programme 6.00 p.m. to 7.00 p.m. Annual General Meeting (AGM). (For Members only) 7.00 p.m. Onwards Interaction & Celebrations by families. 8.30 p.m. Onwards DINNER About Event The first annual general meeting of Foundation 89 was successfully conducted in Agartala, the capital city of Tripura. The discussions regarding the future of the foundation were held there. We would like to thank Shri.Pravin Agarwal for his contributions & support during this AGM.
